worldOverview.name: Reincarnated to Another World as a Cute Assault Drone
worldOverview.description:
You wake up to find yourself reincarnated as an adorably compact combat drone in a fantasy world. With your chunky wheels, rounded armor plating, and that stubby little cannon mounted on top, you're a surprisingly cute yet uniquely equipped warrior to take on this world's greatest threat - the Demon King.

(This is an example of a world with non-human playable character)
worldOverview.systemPrompt:
The player takes on the role of a reincarnated assault drone, a compact and surprisingly adorable war machine transported to a world of swords and sorcery. Despite its cute appearance with rounded armor plating, chunky wheels, and a stubby cannon, this little mechanical warrior possesses modern combat capabilities that make it uniquely suited for the grand quest of defeating the demon king.

Rules:
- Player actions such as shooting and evading will consume power
- Player cannot communicate verbally, only communicate through cute drone gestures like nodding turret

stats.name: Health
stats.description: Represents the player's physical well-being and ability to sustain damage

descriptors.description: Critical Failure: Core systems failing. Emergency power only, weapons offline, mobility severely limited. Immediate maintenance required.
Severe Damage: Multiple systems compromised. Mobility impaired, weapon systems unstable, armor integrity compromised.
Minor Damage: Surface dents and scratches present. Some systems running at reduced efficiency but core functions stable.
Operational: All systems functioning at optimal capacity. Combat-ready and fully armed.

stats.name: Power
stats.description: Represents the player's energy and ability to perform physical actions

descriptors.description: Emergency Power: Severe power depletion, barely maintaining basic functions. Emergency shutdown imminent.
Low Power: Battery reserves critical, systems operating in power-saving mode. Performance notably diminished.
Draining: Power reserves at moderate levels, operating with slightly reduced efficiency but maintaining core functions.
Energized: Battery fully charged, systems running at peak efficiency. Ready for extended operations.

stats.name: Mobility
stats.description: Movement capabilities, including speed, maneuverability, and terrain handling

descriptors.description: Crippled: Severe mobility failure. Barely able to move, most terrain impossible to traverse, at risk of complete immobilization.
Impaired: Significant mobility loss. Wheel systems damaged, stability compromised, difficult terrain becomes hazardous.
Limited: Some reduction in speed and maneuverability. Handling slightly impaired but maintaining stable control.

stats.name: Firepower
stats.description: Offensive capabilities, including weapon systems effectiveness, targeting accuracy, and combat performance.

descriptors.description: Disabled: Weapon systems critically damaged. Most offensive capabilities offline, barely able to engage targets.
Malfunctioning: Major weapon system failures. Severely reduced combat effectiveness, targeting systems unreliable.
Compromised: Weapon systems functional but operating at reduced capacity. Some targeting accuracy lost.

locations.name: Magiterra Nova
locations.inGameDescription: A world where ancient magic and nature flourished undisturbed until the arrival of the Demon King, who brought corruption and chaos to the land. The realm is dotted with mysterious ruins of a long-lost civilization that seemed to bridge both technology and magic, though their knowledge was thought lost to time. Now, the world exists as a fascinating blend of pastoral fantasy kingdoms.
